{"tid":2292183,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"多圖︱泫雅家居look性感又慵懶　DAWN從後攬實女友甜蜜放閃","createTime":"2020-11-19T09:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T11:11:31.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"6ceb36d9333489ca6fa7114792a05b383b066513","tid":2292183,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T09:48:44.000Z","msg":"韓國女歌手泫雅，因為身材姣好而有「性感小野馬」的稱號，她除了經常在Instagram大放自己和男友DAWN的甜蜜日常照之外，亦不忘為粉絲派福利展示傲人身材。今日（19日）泫雅上載一批在更衣室影的代言品牌內衣照，展示出性感又慵懶的在家look。<br />\n<br />\n泫雅先換上一套糖果色的內衣，充滿少女味道活力感十足，零贅肉的身材更是令人相當羨慕。之後泫雅更換上另一套灰色內衣，赤着腳坐在更衣室一角大擺甫士，男友DAWN之後亦加入從後擁抱住泫雅影情侶照，令粉絲大呼甜到漏！"},{"pid":"a8d06aa8a6f84de086dd9056f277e66c74574821","tid":2292183,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T09:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201119/406108883925471232421850.jpeg/gEY5cbYk6RcAPKGmm8pJYsfByJnVPJ4iGLNvnhizb54?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201119%2F406108883925471232421850.jpeg%2FgEY5cbYk6RcAPKGmm8pJYsfByJnVPJ4iGLNvnhizb54%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=181ea0d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201119/406108881530392576207819.jpeg/FmH0fjlqUNE5f_WoNZ4tnPHi45TqRf9bRN0t2kTdLdo?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201119%2F406108881530392576207819.jpeg%2FFmH0fjlqUNE5f_WoNZ4tnPHi45TqRf9bRN0t2kTdLdo%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=dd28ed14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201119/406109675151953920389042.jpeg/6fn_hE6zP982WZV39c-zxa928I_uq2L2ux6eMrsenjI?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201119%2F406109675151953920389042.jpeg%2F6fn_hE6zP982WZV39c-zxa928I_uq2L2ux6eMrsenjI%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=0a87b763&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea6a062f15a522281bbf77fc68a72eb258b2f9c7","tid":2292183,"ui